Compliling Instructions
=======================

In the gameoflifegui.cpp file, change the color/setColor functions to work with
your GameOfLife class. Search for MODIFY in the file.

1) Install qt

$ sudo apt-get install libqt4-dev

2) Compiling

$ cd GameOfLifeGui
$ mkdir build
$ cd build
$ qmake ..
$ make

3) Running

$ ./GameOfLifeGui

Generating Boards
=================

Compile the genboard.cpp file:

$ g++ genboard.cpp -o genboard

Run the genboard program

$ genboard
Usage: ./genboard <filename> <rows> <columns>
$ genboard board50x50.txt 50 50
